Amino Acid Composition Assignment

datafile <- 'Amino Acid Composition.csv'
data <- read.csv(datafile, row.names='X')

Heatmap

library(gplots)
heatmap.2(as.matrix(data), 
          cexRow=0.75,
          cexCol=0.75,
          trace='none',
          main="Raw Data")

heatmap.2(as.matrix(data), 
          cexRow=0.75,
          cexCol=0.75,
          scale="column",
          trace='none',
          main="Normalized Per Food")

heatmap.2(as.matrix(data), 
          cexRow=0.75,
          cexCol=0.75,
          scale="row",
          trace='none',
          main="Normalized to Amino Acids")
